CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 21, 2013

[Cite as 05/21/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-0hio-2060.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2012- 0672. Toledo Bar Assn. v. Royer.

This cause came to be heard upon respondent’s response to the show-cause order issued by this court on April 25, 2013. On consideration thereof, it is ordered that no action shall be taken at this time, provided that respondent enters into a payment plan with the attorney general after this matter is referred for collection.
